      "text": "The definition of peripatetic carries several negative connotations- wandering hither and thither, being itinerant in nature, etc.  But what if the act of walking together was choreographed to connect an idea to a place and experience. In a few weeks a group of educators will be deeply immersed in a program of wellbeing with the theme Inside Out (based on the animated film), followed by a day spent in nature, floating on the Clark Fork of the Columbia River in Montana with the theme of Outside In (based upon using our connection to nature as a way of connecting to ourselves and our collective community)."
    },
