      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "309f6f08594b6591",
      "text": "Although floating on a river is not strictly a peripatetic experience, that day will be designed to build personal awareness through observation of curiosity, feelings and the health of the river.  The arc of learning on that day will include uncovering areas of advocacy and ultimately inspiring each other to take action.  These elements of Awareness, Advocacy and Action are Kavita's definition of agency, and the essence of learning."
